```class Solution {
    public int alternateDigitSum(int n) {
        int sum = 0, sign = 1;
        while (n > 0) {
            int digit = n % 10;
            sum += sign * digit;
            sign *= -1;
            n /= 10;
        }
        return sum;
    }
}```
